{"tid":1916512,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"應承我，今晚我地一齊睇愛回家","createTime":"2020-03-09T02:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T02:23:50.000Z","uid":134997,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eb4069ff25b5ba1647e63eb2847c1c6426cd4cd5","tid":1916512,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"上一集佢地影畢業相話自己係黃絲，我已經原諒咗佢地<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母 係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？<br />\n做咩唔比愛回家既post上熱門？<br />\n如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死<br />\n連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔可以當手足係condom？<br />\n我哋揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可 煲底見！</span></strong></span>[/quote]"},{"pid":"c05f47c0ae42e63e71554d55fc884a94c28b2bb1","tid":1916512,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAJppPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAJppPg.jpg&h=93508a5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1cc04294a7cbcc6f4c773d5b7c3a59d26265f69","tid":1916512,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c05f47c0ae42e63e71554d55fc884a94c28b2bb1","tid":1916512,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAJppPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAJppPg.jpg&h=93508a5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"愛回家係好睇 你老死天氣囝都有睇"},{"pid":"fdf22bf0bd7ddf6aeb7abeab546bd0f49a8b74c3","tid":1916512,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T02:21:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25dbcf8c0c8669049f7b12abe82e4a676ac3e8a4","tid":1916512,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r